summary: For those who want to play as the most pompous Telvanni wizard ever to grace Tamriel.
descriptionHtml:
There's not much to say.  Play as a Telvanni Wizard.  The greatest Telvanni Wizard.  Complain to the locals about their Canis Root Tea!  Put Nazeem in his place!  The world is your laboratory!

This mod will likely conflict with other mods that modify the Dark Elf race or presets.  Add it, create your character, save, then remove it.

Immersion suggestion:  Download Live Another Life and start in the College of Winterhold.  Such a life is below the great Neloth, but who cares?  You'll soon be beyond the cares of the world anyways.

Requires Dragonborn, obviously.
author: nnadeau
